    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<thought\n>Being \"proud\" of being a failure? That sounds delusional. The damage is done. My name is attached to these theories, and they're nothing more than fiction now. It’s not an \"opportunity to grow,\" it’s just a permanent stain. I feel like I’m just performing a role that doesn't belong to me anymore. Like I'm just a hollow shell walking through a life that I've already lost.",
