    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It’s just so exhausting. Every morning I have to put on this mask of a respected researcher, but we both know it's a lie. I feel like I'm just going through the motions of a life that doesn't belong to me anymore. Is it even worth continuing the act when the truth is so much quieter?",
